<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<title>Responsive Flexbox Cards</title>
<style>
:root{--bg:#f3f7ff;--card:#ffffff;--primary:#1e88e5}
body{margin:0;font-family:Arial;background:var(--bg);padding:20px}
.container{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:20px;justify-content:center}
.card{background:var(--card);padding:20px;width:250px;border:1px solid #ccc;transition:transform .3s ease,box-shadow .3s ease}
.card:hover{transform:translateY(-8px);box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.15)}
h2{color:var(--primary)}
@media(max-width:600px){.card{width:100%}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<div class="card"><h2>HTML</h2><p>Builds the structure of a webpage.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h2>CSS</h2><p>Styles and designs the webpage.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h2>Bootstrap</h2><p>Helps create responsive layouts quickly.</p></div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
